https://www.kipr.org/gcer/register-gcer
You will need to be logged into your KIPR account in order to view this page though.

@everyone GCER registration is live! Even if your team doesn't know exactly who is going yet, your team can still register individual members or coaches.
https://botball-swag.myshopify.com/products/2022-global-conference-on-educational-robotics

We are still finishing up some changes for scoring and will be putting those out sometime this week. We never lower the number of points for something for GCER so if your team has a robot that scores high already, you'll still be scoring that much at GCER!

hardStop() 
